job_history.work_description: Managed and lead a team of professional recruiters through coaching and training. Developed and execute recruiting plans and recruiting outreach programs Partnered with Hiring Managers, and Director of HR to determine hiring needs and strategies.

Managed a team of recruiters and report on recruiting performance Advise Hiring Managers on interviewing techniques Research and choose different healthcare job advertising options Identify and acquire top talent for: different clinical and none clinical positions.
Work collaboratively with Program Managers, Directors Sales Personnel, Clients and Candidates in managing requisitions and matching the right candidates to positions.

Responsible for assisting HR with internal compliance on all teachers, therapists and social workers, ensuring that all appropriate billing and session/progress notes and documents were received and submitted within deadlines.
Provided resource management and recruitment to fill therapy job openings, including candidate sourcing, screening, interviewing and checking.

Oversaw all aspects of staff performance, conducted performance evaluation, enforced progressive discipline and mediated staff disputes and grievance procedures in accordance with state and federal laws.

skills.name: Recruitment
skills.explanation: Has extensive experience in recruitment, including developing and executing recruiting plans, managing teams of recruiters, and advising hiring managers, indicating expert-level mastery.

skills.name: Leadership
skills.explanation: Has led teams of recruiters and program coordinators, and has experience with performance evaluations, progressive discipline, and grievance procedures, indicating expert-level mastery.

skills.name: Human Resource Management
skills.explanation: Has experience with internal compliance, resource management, and recruitment, suggesting strong proficiency in human resource management.

skills.name: Communication
skills.explanation: Has a degree in Communications and has worked in roles that require effective communication, such as recruitment and human resource management, indicating a solid working proficiency.

skills.name: Project Management
skills.explanation: Has experience with managing requisitions and matching candidates to positions, but the extent of project management experience is not clear, suggesting some practical experience.

skills.explanation: Has a certificate in Healthcare Compliance, but the extent of practical experience is not clear, suggesting some practical experience.
